keep.echo_system: All files in src/echo/* - this is your user-facing memory
keep.qlib_backend: All files in backend/qlib/* - this is your vault interface
keep.bridge_files: Files that connect ECHO and QLIB

migrate.components_memory: Move memory logic from components/* to appropriate ECHO/QLIB locations
migrate.duplicate_functions: Consolidate duplicate implementations between old and new systems

delete.orphaned_files: Files with no imports and no exports
delete.old_diagnostics: Old diagnostic and test files from previous attempts
